  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Line <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math> is defined by <math alttext=\"y equals 6 x plus 4\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>y</mi>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mn>6</mn>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t\t<mn>4</mn>\n\t</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</math>. Line <math alttext=\"j\"><mi>j</mi>\n</math> is parallel to line <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math> in the&nbsp;<em>xy</em>-plane and passes through the point <math alttext=\"left parenthesis 0 comma 5 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mrow><mn>5</mn></mrow></mrow></mfenced></math>. Which equation defines line <math alttext=\"j\"><mi>j</mi>\n</math>?&nbsp;</p>",
